潮，而过量的大学生供应恰好遇上了日本就业冰河时期。 ——《失落的 20 年》 未来 10 年，我国也将迎来与日本上世纪 90 年代类似的大学生就业高峰。 面对相同的就业困境，回顾日本这段学历贬值的历史，对于今天的我们而言或许有些借鉴意义。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-3bf320003431c8341ffb8a17a12a6db8_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/8880483066"}}, "attached_info": "CkEI89bktZqmvOZOEAMaCTExMjc1MjUyNiC4w+67BjAAOO8BQBJyCjg4ODA0ODMwNjZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1736327305.557326", "card_id": "Q_612556266", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你怎么看待 Deft 选手说的「人生在世，其实不太需要接受别人的建议，只有经历了才知道」?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-478c48d05720fb4e23e8ef58a57d4e23_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/612556266"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I89bktZqmvOZOEAMaCDk4NDA0NDQ5IKzI1KUGMAA4JEATcgk2MTI1NTYyNjZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1736327305.557576", "card_id": "Q_8944712977", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 152}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "京东家政投入 10 亿重金，招募十万名保洁师，此举有何考量？这在家政行业的吸引力有多大？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "1 月 7 日，京东家政发布十万人招募计划，面向百县干镇招募 10 万名保洁师。10 亿元重金！京东家政将招募十万名保洁师"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-20d591916792f374d798383d601350f5_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/8944712977"}}, "att